  "description": "<b>美国艺电游戏公司(EA)近日<a href=\"http://www.neowin.net/forum/topic/1155693-ea-removing-online-pass-requirement-for-existing-games/\" target=\"_blank\">放弃</a>了在当前一代游戏主机上的\"多人游戏在线认证\"要求，但这使得某些人推测该公司将会转而寻求Xbox One上的数字版权管理(DRM)技术</b>。不过EA首席运营官Peter Moore澄清，事情并非如此。Peter Moore对<a href=\"http://www.polygon.com/2013/6/11/4421314/electronic-arts-talks-drm-and-used-games\" target=\"_blank\">Polygon</a>说，这种猜测是\"完全错误的\"，并指出，该公司放弃在线认证的决定与即将到来的下一代游戏主机毫不相干。<br /><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d36483a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240877.htm&amp;t=EA%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B2%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%89%88%E6%9D%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240877.htm&amp;t=EA%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B2%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%89%88%E6%9D%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240877.htm&amp;t=EA%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B2%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%89%88%E6%9D%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240877.htm&amp;t=EA%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B2%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82Xbox+One%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%89%88%E6%9D%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img bo