  "description": "<b>据外媒报道，近日，爱尔兰法院下令，要求国内的6家主要互联网服务提供商(ISP)屏蔽掉“海盗湾(The Priate Bay)”网站。</b>据悉，这一规定的出台源于4家音乐公司对“海盗湾”的投诉。4家音乐公司指出，每个月有近20万用户（相当于8%的爱尔兰互联网用户）都会访问“海盗湾”并下载被分享到该平台上的音乐文件，而ISP却没有对此采取任何措施。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d364838/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240878.htm&amp;t=%E7%88%B1%E5%B0%94%E5%85%B0%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4+%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82ISP%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD%E2%80%9C%E6%B5%B7%E7%9B%97%E6%B9%BE%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240878.htm&amp;t=%E7%88%B1%E5%B0%94%E5%85%B0%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4+%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82ISP%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD%E2%80%9C%E6%B5%B7%E7%9B%97%E6%B9%BE%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240878.htm&amp;t=%E7%88%B1%E5%B0%94%E5%85%B0%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4+%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82ISP%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD%E2%80%9C%E6%B5%B7%E7%9B%97%E6%B9%BE%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240878.htm&amp;t=%E7%88%B1%E5%B0%94%E5%85%B0%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4+%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82ISP%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD%E2%80%9C%E6%B5%B7%E7%9B%97%E6%B9%BE%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240878.htm&amp;t=%E7%88%B1%E5%B0%94%E5%85%B0